---
const { t } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="cycle">
	<div class="title">
		<h1>不只是一次合作</h1>
		<h1>而是一場能持續十年、二十年的循環。</h1>
		<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Cycle.svg" alt="" id='Cycle_img'/>
		<!-- mobile Text -->
		<div class="mobileCycleText ">
			<div class="title-with-arrow">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="23" height="19" viewBox="0 0 23 19" fill="none">
					<path d="M2 10.4998C6.33333 9.8331 16.1 8.69976 20.5 9.49976C21.1005 9.60895 21.3066 9.60164 21.5 9.5M13 2C16.7419 4.44657 21.5 9.5 21.5 9.5M21.5 9.5C20.6095 10.6667 18.6 13.8 17 17" stroke="#00D959" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
				</svg>
				<h3 class="emfont-XiaoLai">發覺新秀</h3>
			</div>
			<p>舉辦年會、黑客松，提供各領域人才展現自我與交流所學的舞台。</p>

			<div class="title-with-arrow">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="23" height="19" viewBox="0 0 23 19" fill="none">
					<path d="M2 10.4998C6.33333 9.8331 16.1 8.69976 20.5 9.49976C21.1005 9.60895 21.3066 9.60164 21.5 9.5M13 2C16.7419 4.44657 21.5 9.5 21.5 9.5M21.5 9.5C20.6095 10.6667 18.6 13.8 17 17" stroke="#00D959" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
				</svg>
				<h3 class="emfont-XiaoLai">培育人才</h3>
			</div>
			<p>推動教育公平、促進產學交流，培養組織與領導能力</p>
			
			<div class="title-with-arrow">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="23" height="19" viewBox="0 0 23 19" fill="none">
					<path d="M2 10.4998C6.33333 9.8331 16.1 8.69976 20.5 9.49976C21.1005 9.60895 21.3066 9.60164 21.5 9.5M13 2C16.7419 4.44657 21.5 9.5 21.5 9.5M21.5 9.5C20.6095 10.6667 18.6 13.8 17 17" stroke="#00D959" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
				</svg>
				<h3 class="emfont-XiaoLai">創造影響</h3>
			</div>
			<p>尋找使用者與徵才，搶佔年輕開發者的心</p>
		</div>

		<div class="slogan">
			<p>參與 SITCON 不只是曝光，而是成為社群的一部分</br>從第一場 SITCON 到第一個專案團隊，企業與人才的故事由你啟動。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="eateateat">
			<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" class="Hungry_img"/>
			<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" class="Hungry_img"/>
			<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" class="Hungry_img"/>
			<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" class="Hungry_img"/>
		</div>	
		<div class="container">
			<div id='no_hungry'>
				<p>消除飢餓</p>
				<p>開會前後或沒事會揪團去吃好吃的。</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
.title{
	text-align: center
}

#Cycle_img{
	padding-top: 3.06rem;
	padding-bottom: 1.39rem;
}

.mobileCycleText {
	display: none;
}

.eateateat{
	display: inline-flex;
	align-items: center;
	gap: 1.4375rem;
	padding-top: 5.44rem;
}

.Hungry_img {
	opacity: 0.6;
	transform: scale(1);
	transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
	animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-in-out forwards;
}

.Hungry_img:nth-child(1) {
	animation-delay: 0.1s;
}

.Hungry_img:nth-child(2) {
	animation-delay: 0.2s;
}

.Hungry_img:nth-child(3) {
	animation-delay: 0.3s;
}

.Hungry_img:nth-child(4) {
	animation-delay: 0.4s;
}

.Hungry_img:hover {
	transform: scale(1.1);
	opacity: 1;
}

#no_hungry {
	max-width: 600px;
	margin: 2rem auto;
	text-align: left;
	padding: 0 2rem;
}

#no_hungry p:first-child {
	font-size: 1.9375rem;
}

#no_hungry p:last-child {
	font-size: 1.3125rem;
}

.container {
	display: flex;
	justify-content: center; 
}

.container > div {
	border-radius: 8px;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
	#Cycle_img {
		content: url("/cfs/Cycle/mobileCycle.svg");
		width: 70%;
		height: auto;
	}
	
	.mobileCycleText {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: flex-start; 
		max-width: 600px; 
		margin: 2rem auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		text-align: left;
	}
	
	.mobileCycleText .title-with-arrow {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center; 
		gap: 0.5rem; 
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.mobileCycleText svg {
		flex-shrink: 0; 
	}
	
	.mobileCycleText h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: bold;

	}
	
	.mobileCycleText p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
		color: #333;
		padding-bottom: 1em;
	}
	
	.title h1 {
		font-size: 1.2rem; 
	}
	.slogan p{
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		padding: 2rem;
	}	
	.Hungry_img {
		width: 5rem; 
		height: auto;
	}
	
	.eateateat {
		gap: 1rem; 
		padding: 0.8rem;
	}
	
	#no_hungry p:first-child {
		font-size: 1.2rem; 
	}
	
	#no_hungry p:last-child {
		font-size: 1rem; 
	}
}
</style>
